sp_scores.title: Defeat the Black Waltz 3 without being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: Watch out for Black Waltz 3's powerful spells, kupo! The thing's immune to Silence, so put up a Reflect and bounce that bad mojo right back at him!
tip_battle.title: Black Waltz 3

dungeons.epilogue: Blank was petrified saving Garnet and the others in the Evil Forest, so Marcus headed for Treno to find a cure. Feeling responsible for Blank’s fate, Garnet’s party joined him. On the way, they defeated Black Waltz 3.
dungeons.name: South Gate
dungeons.prologue: Garnet’s party reunites with Marcus of Tantalus, and heads for Treno to find the cure for their petrified friend, Blank.

sp_scores.title: Defeat the Masked Man without being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: The Masked Man only uses physical attacks, kupo! Abilities like Power Break and Protect will make him much easier to defeat!
tip_battle.title: Masked Man

sp_scores.title: Defeat Steiner without being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: Steiner only uses physical attacks, kupo! Abilities like Power Break and Protect will take the bite out of his hits!
tip_battle.title: Steiner

sp_scores.title: Defeat Steiner without being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: Steiner only uses physical attacks, kupo! Abilities like Power Break and Protect will take the bite out of his hits!
tip_battle.title: Steiner, Haagen, and Weimar

sp_scores.title: Defeat Steiner before the bomb self-destructs.
Defeat Steiner and the bomb without being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: If the bomb goes off, it will hit the whole party for major damage, kupo! Either bring down Steiner before it blows up, or heal everyone up before it goes kaboom!
tip_battle.title: Steiner & The Bomb

dungeons.epilogue: Zidane went backstage after Garnet, only to have her request her own kidnapping. The Tantalus troupe involved Garnet and Vivi in their performance to escape Steiner, leaving Alexandria aboard the M.S. Prima Vista, but the theater ship was brought down by cannon fire from the castle and crashed in the Evil Forest.
dungeons.name: M.S. Prima Vista
dungeons.prologue: Our story begins with a performance in celebration of Princess Garnet's birthday that brings Zidane, Vivi, and the princess together.

sp_scores.title: Defeat Beatrix without being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: It's only a matter of time before Beatrix unleashes her powerful Stock Break ability, hitting the entire party for tons of damage! Use Slow on her to buy as much time as you can, kupo!
tip_battle.title: Beatrix

dungeons.epilogue: In the palace, the party found Queen Brahne, General Beatrix, and the mysterious Kuja. Hearing that the king had taken refuge in Cleyra, the queen left the capital, leaving behind Kuja, who displayed concern about Zidane.
dungeons.name: Burmecia
dungeons.prologue: The black mages have left the capital of Burmecia in ruins. Freya is furious at the destruction, and the party hurries to the palace.

sp_scores.title: Defeat the Black Waltz 2 without being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: When Black Waltz 2's HP gets low, it will counter certain elemental magic attacks by casting a spell of the same element that hits the entire party, kupo! Switch to physical attacks once you get its HP low enough!
tip_battle.title: Black Waltz 2

dungeons.epilogue: Vivi was taken away by a villager in Dali, but when Zidane and Dagger went looking for him, they discovered many other black mages, all identical to their friend. The villagers of Dali were manufacturing black mages for Alexandria. Reunited, the party fought off the assassin Black Waltz 2 and boarded a cargo ship.
dungeons.name: Village of Dali
dungeons.prologue: After escaping pursuit and passing along the slippery paths of the Ice Cavern, Garnet takes the name Dagger to conceal her identity. The party arrives in the small village of Dali.

sp_scores.title: Exploit Ralvurahva's weakness to ice attacks.

tip_battle.message: Ralvurahva lays the debuffs on thick, kupo, so have Esuna at the ready! Oh, and hit him with some ice attacks while you're at it. He hates those!
tip_battle.title: Ralvurahva

dungeons.epilogue: Garnet was reunited with her old tutor, Doctor Tot, and the next day, he showed them the way to Gargan Roo, an ancient transport network allowing them quick access to Alexandria. Boarding the Gargant, they reached the castle, but Garnet went missing soon after their arrival.
dungeons.name: Gargan Roo
dungeons.prologue: The party enters a manse in search of the Supersoft, where they are reunited with Doctor Tot, who leads them to Gargan Roo.

sp_scores.title: Exploit Ralvuimago's weakness to ice attacks.

tip_battle.message: Hit Ralvuimago with a physical attack and he'll go into defense mode, kupo. When he does that, watch out! Hit him with another physical attack and he'll lay down the hurt on your whole party with Power of the Land. Better to take advantage of his weakness to ice magic before that happens, kupo!
tip_battle.title: Ralvuimago

dungeons.epilogue: Zidane’s party was escaping with Garnet when they met Marcus and the revived Blank, who joined their ranks. Together, they took the Gargant out of the castle, but spooked by its mortal enemy, the Ralvuimago, the Gargant sped past their destination of Treno and crashed.
dungeons.name: Alexandria Castle, Part 3
dungeons.prologue: With help from Beatrix and the others, Zidane’s party escapes from Alexandria Castle, meeting Marcus and Blank.

sp_scores.title: Defeat Beatrix without being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: Give Beatrix enough time and she'll hit the whole party with Climhazzard, kupo, reducing everyone down to 1 HP! If you can take her down before then, by all means! But just in case you can't, be sure to heal up right after Climhazzard hits, kupo! You might want to bring more than one character capable of healing everyone in the party, just to be safe.
tip_battle.title: Beatrix

dungeons.epilogue: Beatrix was going to stop Zidane’s party, but when she saw Garnet’s limp form, she realized the error of her ways, and, reviving Garnet, she joined the party's fight against her former mistress, Brahne. While Freya, Beatrix, and Steiner held off their pursuers, Zidane’s party made their escape.
dungeons.name: Alexandria Castle, Part 2
dungeons.prologue: Zidane's party defeats Zorn and Thorn and is on its way out of the castle when Beatrix appears before them.

sp_scores.title: Exploit Ralvurahva's weakness to ice attacks.

tip_battle.message: Ralvurahva lays the debuffs on thick, kupo, so have Esuna at the ready! Oh, and hit him with some ice attacks while you're at it. He hates those!
tip_battle.title: Ralvurahva

dungeons.epilogue: Garnet was reunited with her old tutor, Doctor Tot, and the next day, he showed them the way to Gargan Roo, an ancient transport network allowing them quick access to Alexandria. Boarding the Gargant, they reached the castle, but Garnet went missing soon after their arrival.
dungeons.name: Gargan Roo
dungeons.prologue: The party enters a manse in search of the Supersoft, where they are reunited with Doctor Tot, who leads them to Gargan Roo.

sp_scores.title: Defeat Beatrix without being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: Give Beatrix enough time and she'll hit your whole party with a nasty Stock Break, kupo! My advice? Slow her down as much as possible to buy yourself time! Beware, though, kupo. She has more tricks in her bag, and no known weaknesses! Try using Power Break and Armor Break to even the odds!
tip_battle.title: Beatrix

dungeons.epilogue: Back in the city, the party led the survivors to the Cathedral, where Sir Fratley arrived to aid them. Freya was devastated to learn that he had suffered amnesia and remembered nothing of their love. General Beatrix then appeared, stealing the Desert Star and fleeing back to her ship. Zidane’s party gave chase, but as they left Cleyra, Brahne summoned Odin and destroyed the city.
dungeons.name: Cleyra Cathedral
dungeons.prologue: Zidane’s party heads down the trunk of the tree supporting Cleyra, hoping to find whatever’s stopping the sandstorm. While they are gone, black mages enter the city from the Red Rose and commence their attack.

sp_scores.title: Defeat the Masked Man without being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: The Masked Man only uses physical attacks, kupo! Abilities like Power Break and Protect will make him much easier to defeat!
tip_battle.title: Masked Man

sp_scores.title: Defeat Steiner without being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: Steiner only uses physical attacks, kupo! Abilities like Power Break and Protect will take the bite out of his hits!
tip_battle.title: Steiner

sp_scores.title: Defeat Steiner without being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: Steiner only uses physical attacks, kupo! Abilities like Power Break and Protect will take the bite out of his hits!
tip_battle.title: Steiner, Haagen, and Weimar

sp_scores.title: Defeat Steiner before the bomb self-destructs.
Defeat Steiner and the bomb without being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: If the bomb goes off, it will hit the whole party for major damage, kupo! Either bring down Steiner before it blows up, or heal everyone up before it goes kaboom!
tip_battle.title: Steiner & The Bomb

Prima Vista, but the theater ship was brought down by cannon fire from the castle and crashed in the Evil Forest.
dungeons.name: M.S. Prima Vista
dungeons.prologue: Our story begins with a performance in celebration of Princess Garnet's birthday that brings Zidane, Vivi, and the princess together.

sp_scores.title: Exploit Gizamaluk's weakness to lightning attacks.
Exploit Gizamaluk's weakness to wind attacks.

tip_battle.message: Gizamaluk counterattacks with Lunge if you hit it with physical attacks! And if you hit it with magic, it will Silence you, kupo! To sidestep all these counterattacks, try hitting it with debuffs first!
tip_battle.title: Gizamaluk

dungeons.epilogue: The party arrived at Gizamaluk's Grotto on their way to Burmecia, seeing the signs of the black mage attack everywhere. With their new companion, Quina, Zidane's party had figured out the system of bells allowing passage through the grotto, when the black mage commanders Zorn and Thorn attacked. Surviving this, the party defeated the insane Gizamaluk and made their way out.
dungeons.name: Gizamaluk's Grotto
dungeons.prologue: In Lindblum, Zidane is reunited with his old friend Freya, and learns that her homeland, Burmecia, is under attack by an army of black mages.

sp_scores.title: Exploit the Prison Cage's weakness to fire attacks.

tip_battle.message: Party members trapped by Prison Cage have their HP drained away every turn, kupo! The worst part is, there's no way to break them out! The best thing to do is cast Regen on them to keep them alive until they get out!
tip_battle.title: Prison Cage

sp_scores.title: Exploit the Plant Brain's weakness to fire attacks.
Defeat the Plant Brain without being KO'd.

tip_battle.message: Plant Brain uses its Pollen ability at the beginning of battle to Blind the entire party, kupo! Either equip accessories that protect against Blindness, or have a character with the Blindna ability ready to go!
tip_battle.title: Plant Brain

dungeons.epilogue: With Blank's assistance, Zidane's party succeeded in rescuing Garnet from Plant Brain. As the forest turned to stone around them, Blank sacrificed himself to help the rest escape the Evil Forest.
dungeons.name: Evil Forest
dungeons.prologue: Garnet has been taken captive, and Zidane, Vivi, and Steiner must make their way through the Evil Forest to find her.

sp_scores.title: Defeat Zorn and Thorn without being KO'd.
Defeat Zorn before he uses Meteorite.
Defeat Thorn before he uses Light Flare.

tip_battle.message: Thorn and Zorn have a nasty habit of powering each other up, kupo, and the one who gets empowered will start casting spells, so look out! Here's a tip: attack the one who's empowered and he'll lose power, and the ability to cast magic! Pretty nifty, eh, kupo?
tip_battle.title: Thorn and Zorn

dungeons.epilogue: Steiner and Marcus cooperated to break free of their imprisonment, rejoining Zidane’s party. They encountered Zorn and Thorn in the castle chapel, overcoming them with their combined strength, and finally found Garnet, who was unconscious, having been stripped of her summons by Brahne’s orders.
dungeons.name: Alexandria Castle, Part 1
dungeons.prologue: Zidane's party uses the magical pods aboard the Red Rose to teleport to Alexandria Castle where they reunite with Steiner to search for Garnet.

sp_scores.title: Win without the White Mage being KO'd.
Defeat Beatrix without being KO'd.

sp_scores.title: Exploit the Antlion's weakness to ice attacks.

tip_battle.message: Hit an Antlion with physical attacks and he'll hit right back with an appropriately-named Counter Horn, kupo! Here's a tip: use ice magic against him! And if his Trouble Mucus has anyone in your party confused, attack them to unconfuse them, pronto!
tip_battle.title: Antlion

dungeons.epilogue: Zidane and the others saved Puck from the Antlion in Cleyra, and warned the people there of the coming attack. But when the people of Cleyra conducted a ceremony to strengthen the sandstorm protecting their town, the winds mysteriously quieted, leading the king of Burmecia to suspect enemy action.
dungeons.name: Cleyra Sandpit
dungeons.prologue: Hoping to avoid another disaster such as the one which befell Burmecia, Zidane’s party heads to Cleyra where they find many of the Burmecian survivors have taken refuge.
